name: Disposable Breathing Space Cover
descr:
Disposable breathing space cover has a cross nick in the middle which will be suitable to use on any shape of breathing space.

Inexpensive price disposable breathing space cover has a cross nick in the middle
which will be suitable to use on any shape of breathing space. Asepsis is used to avoid
bacterial infection and anaphylaxis during breath. Soft and thick non-woven fabric made.
 
Dimensions: 42 x 32 cm.
 
Packaging: 100 pcs/pack and 10 packs/box.
